overhead here is all in function call marshalling.

   text	   data	    bss	    dec	    hex	filename
   2077	      0	      0	   2077	    81d fs/xfs/libxfs/xfs_types.o.orig
   2197	      0	      0	   2197	    895	fs/xfs/libxfs/xfs_types.o

